##### 26 Validating payments authorised by Patea Harbour Board in connection with its dissolution
    
*   Whereas the Patea Harbour Board (in this section referred to as the **Board**) was dissolved on 1 September 1965, by [section 4(3)][56] of the Taranaki Harbours Act 1965:
    
