    *   (a) a sum not exceeding 200 pounds to meet the cost of a function to mark the occasion of the dissolution of the Board and the abolition of the Patea Harbour District; and
    
    *   (b) a sum of 187 pounds 10 shillings to the Secretary of the Board as a retiring allowance; and
    
